tamago without telling you.

504
00:29:14.544 --> 00:29:16.981
It's fine. I've been meaning to sell it.

505
00:29:17.005 --> 00:29:19.174
Yeah. he really didn't need to.

506
00:29:19.716 --> 00:29:22.469
Let him think he saved the day. okay?

507
00:29:23.011 --> 00:29:24.488
He needs it.

508
00:29:24.512 --> 00:29:25.512
Okay.

509
00:29:25.930 --> 00:29:27.640
You're looking much better.

510
00:29:28.892 --> 00:29:30.435
My body heals quickly.

511
00:29:32.771 --> 00:29:35.916
Are you sure you're done?
We can keep shopping.

512
00:29:35.940 --> 00:29:37.793
Anything you want? It's on me.

513
00:29:37.817 --> 00:29:41.738
You've always been so generous.
and I'm sure you'll continue to be.

514
00:29:43.281 --> 00:29:46.385
Fumi. I wanted to address
the elephant in the room.

515
00:29:46.409 --> 00:29:47.928
- Elephant?
- Yeah.

516
00:29:47.952 --> 00:29:49.412
I don't see an elephant.

517
00:29:50.538 --> 00:29:55.502
I see shapes and swirls and patterns.

518
00:29:59.130 --> 00:30:02.008
Haru and I loved each other deeply.

519
00:30:02.884 --> 00:30:05.303
We wanted the same things out of life.

520
00:30:06.888 --> 00:30:08.598
We achieved so much together.

521
00:30:09.933 --> 00:30:12.268
But financial stability
was not one of them.

522
00:30:13.311 --> 00:30:15.480
There was a time when
we worried over money.

523
00:30:16.189 --> 00:30:18.316
but he taught me
something very important.

524
00:30:19.108 --> 00:30:21.110
The moment you begin to worry.

525
00:30:21.945 --> 00:30:24.322
the moment you acknowledge the worry.

526
00:30:25.073 --> 00:30:27.158
you solidify it into existence.

527
00:30:27.909 --> 00:30:29.828
which is why we chose to ignore.

528
00:30:30.370 --> 00:30:32.080
and ignore we did.

529
00:30:34.415 --> 00:30:36.125
I'm not sure I follow.

530
00:30:37.335 --> 00:30:38.586
Well. look at me now.

531
00:30:39.128 --> 00:30:40.630
Buying everything I want.

532
00:30:41.256 --> 00:30:43.424
Amy. all you have is perception.

533
00:30:44.008 --> 00:30:45.945
There is no objective truth.

534
00:30:45.969 --> 00:30:48.429
You create the truth you want to inhabit.

535
00:30:50.640 --> 00:30:52.851
So. what do you want for your family?

536
00:30:54.185 --> 00:30:56.187
What do you want for yourself?

537
00:31:07.782 --> 00:31:09.284
Where the fuck is Isaac?

538
00:31:16.541 --> 00:31:17.643
You fucking snake.

539
00:31:17.667 --> 00:31:18.561
What?

540
00:31:18.585 --> 00:31:19.645
What's going on?

541
00:31:19.669 --> 00:31:20.938
I'm in fucking jail!

542
00:31:20.962 --> 00:31:22.338
Looking at five to ten.

543
00:31:22.755 --> 00:31:25.109
I don't understand. What happened?

544
00:31:25.133 --> 00:31:27.027
What happened? You sold me out.

545
00:31:27.051 --> 00:31:29.029
I don't know what you're talking about.

546
00:31:29.053 --> 00:31:30.781
I just got the call and I came here.

547
00:31:30.805 --> 00:31:32.765
Like. I'm completely in the dark.

548
00:31:36.144 --> 00:31:38.229
Let's go. Danny!

549
00:31:40.982 --> 00:31:42.317
There it is.

550
00:31:52.577 --> 00:31:55.097
My lawyer had me in the
clear. She had it all planned out.

551
00:31:55.121 --> 00:31:57.600
Did your lawyer fuck up? Do you
need me to get you a new one?

552
00:31:57.624 --> 00:32:00.644
It's your fucking road rage shit!
The fucking cops think I did it.

553
00:32:00.668 --> 00:32:02.605
My parole's fucked!

554
00:32:02.629 --> 00:32:03.731
Fucked!

555
00:32:03.755 --> 00:32:06.191
Who else would've sold me
out besides you? Who else?

556
00:32:06.215 --> 00:32:11.155
Hey. first of all. that... come on. I
would never even think to do that.

557
00:32:11.179 --> 00:32:14.891
That's some diabolical mastermind
shit. I can't even think that far out.

558
00:32:17.936 --> 00:32:19.288
Wait. dude.

559
00:32:19.312 --> 00:32:20.688
For the lord.

560
00:32:22.023 --> 00:32:23.751
- Next one!
- That's all right!

561
00:32:23.775 --> 00:32:24.817
Word of god!

562
00:32:27.779 --> 00:32:28.779
Focus!

563
00:32:29.280 --> 00:32:30.633
Get the ball!

564
00:32:30.657 --> 00:32:33.826
I bet Amy saw the
license plate on the truck.

565
00:32:34.410 --> 00:32:35.912
And it's under your name.

566
00:32:37.205 --> 00:32:38.206
Fuck.

567
00:32:39.457 --> 00:32:41.268
You didn't tell them it was me. right?

568
00:32:41.292 --> 00:32:44.146
I did. I told them right away.
The cops didn't believe me.

569
00:32:44.170 --> 00:32:46.231
Man. 'Cause your record?

570
00:32:46.255 --> 00:32:48.943
Just say you were driving.
man. Just say you were driving.

571
00:32:48.967 --> 00:32:51.469
The Filipinos turned on
me. I gotta get out of here!

572
00:32:53.638 --> 00:32:54.722
Right.

573
00:32:56.224 --> 00:32:58.702
Yeah. dude. Yeah. of course.

574
00:32:58.726 --> 00:33:00.621
I'll vouch for you. yeah. Okay?

575
00:33:00.645 --> 00:33:01.896
I'll take the fall.

576
00:33:10.780 --> 00:33:12.490
Fucking fuck!

577
00:33:14.325 --> 00:33:15.511
I got you. man.

578
00:33:15.535 --> 00:33:16.828
Anything you need.

579
00:33:17.412 --> 00:33:18.830
Dude. you're driving...

580
00:33:19.622 --> 00:33:21.165
I'm just along for the ride.

581
00:33:21.916 --> 00:33:23.084
He's open! He's open!

582
00:33:39.976 --> 00:33:42.186
What the fuck?!
